s the said period is extended by the Collector from time to time, the permission granted shall be deemed to have lapsed. </p><p> 5. शुलके के भुगतान की जिम्मेदारी :- आवेदक उक्त भूमि पर लगाए जानेवाले सभी करों, उपशुल्कों तथा उपकारों का भुगतान करेग। </p><p> Liability for rates: -The applicant shall pay all taxes, rales and cesses leviable on the said land. </p><p> 6. दण्ड विधि (क): यदि आवेदक पूर्वोक्त किसी भी शर्त का उल्लधन करता है, तो समाहर्ता बिना किसी पूर्वाग्रह के उक्त कोड के उपबंधों के तहत लागू दण्ड प्रभारित कर सकते है एवं ऐसे शुल्क एवं निधारत मूल्य का भुगतान करने पर उक्त प्लॉट को आवेदक के नाम जारी रख सकते ह। </p><p> Penalty clause - - (a) If the applicant contravenes any of the foregoing conditions the Collector may, without prejudice to any other penalty to which the applicant may be liable under the provisions of the said Code continue the said plot in the occupation of the applicant on payment of such fine and assessment as he may direct. </p><p>applicant on payment of such fine and assessment as he may direct. (ख) उपखण्ड (क) मे ऐसा वृछ होते हुए भी इसके बारे मे समाहर्ता द्वारा विनिर्दिष्ट ऐसी समय सीमा के भीतर किसी भवन के हटाने या बनाए गए भवन या संरचना मे परिवर्तन करने या इस अनुमति के उपन्धो के प्रतिकूल उपयोग करने पर निर्देश देना समाहर्ता के लिए विधि-सम्मत हॉगा तथा यदि ऐसे भवन को हटाया या इसमें परिवर्तन नहीं किया जाता है , तो यह करने के लिए आने वाली लागत को आवेदक से भू-राजस्वा के रूप मे वसूली जाएगी । </p><p>(b) Notwithstanding anything contained in sub-clause (a) it shall be lawful for the Collector to direct the removal or alteration of any building or structure erected or use contrary to the provisions of this grant within such time as specified in that behalf by the Collector, and on such removal or alteration not being carried out and recover the cost of carrying out the same from the applicant as on arrears of land revenue</p><p> 7. लागू कोड उपलब्ध : इसमें दिए गए उपबंधनो के सिवाय उक्त कोड तथा उसके तहत बनाई गयी नियमावली के उपबंधनो की शर्तो के तहत अनुमति दी जाएगी। </p><p> Code provision applicable - Save as herein provided the grant shall be subject to the provisions of the said Code and rules thereunder. </p><p> समाहर्ता , दमन ने निम्नलिखित के सशय मे प्रशासक दमन एवं दीव की ओर से अपने हस्ताक्षर एवं कार्यालय मुहर प्रदान की है तथा आवदक ने दिनाक <span style="text-decoration:underline;"> ' . $data["18"] . ' </span>  के अपने हस्ताक्षर किये है। </p><p> In witness whereof Collector, Daman, has hereunto set his hand and seal of his Office on behalf of the Administrator of Daman & Diu and the applicant has also hereunto set his hand <span style="text-decoration:underline;"> ' . $data["19"] . ' </span> " day of April, 2021 </p>(SURESHCHANDRA RAMANLAL DESAI) आवेदक के हस्ताक्षर / Signature of the applicant <p> साक्षियों के हस्ताक्षर 1.<span style="text-decoration:underline;"> ' . $data["20"] . ' </span>  </p><p> (Signature and designation of witnesses) 2. <span style="text-decoration:underline;"> ' . $data["21"] . ' </span>  </p><p> (साक्षियों के हस्ताक्षर एवं पदनाम) 1. <span style="text-decoration:underline;"> ' . $data["22"] . ' </span>  </p><p> (Signature and designation of witnesses) 2. <span style="text-decoration:underline;"> ' . $data["23"] . ' </span>  </p><p> हम यह घोषणा करते है कि श्री <span style="text-decoration:underline;"> ' . $data["24"] . ' </span>  जिन्होंने इस सनद पर हस्ताक्षर किये है हमारी जानकारी के अनुसार ये वही व्यक्ति है जिसने हमारे समक्ष अपने हस्ताक्षर किये है। </p><p> We declare that Shri/Smt. <span style="text-decoration:underline;"> ' . $data["25"] . ' </span>  who have signed this Sanad is, to our personal knowledge, the person he represent himself to be and that he /she has affixed his signature hereto in our presence. </p></div><table style="width: 100%;"> <tr> <td style="width: 70%;font-size:20px;"></td><td style="width: 30%;font-size:20px;"> <p> 1. <span style="text-decoration:underline;"> ' . $data["26"] . ' </span>  </p><p> 2. <span style="text-decoration:underline;"> ' . $data["27"] . ' </span>  </p></td></tr></table> </div></body></html>';
    }
    
    public function form2($data = array()) {
        // $html = '<!doctype html><html lang="en"><head> <meta charset="utf-8"> <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/> <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no"> <title>Codeigniter 4 PDF Example - positronx.io</title> <style>*{font-family: DejaVu Sans; font-size: 12px;}p, li, ol{font-size: 20px;}li{margin: 5px auto;}h3{font-size: 25px;}</style></head><body> <div style="width: 95%; margin:0 auto 0;font-size:20px;"> <p align="center">U.T. Administration of Dadra & Nagar Haveli and Daman & Diu</p><p align="center">Office of the Collector </p><p align="center">Revenue Section , Daman - 396 220</p><div style="height:40px;"></div><table style="width: 100%;"> <tr> <td style="width: 80%;font-size:20px;">Order No. </td><td style="width: 20%;font-size:20px;">Dated:- </td></tr></table> <div> <p>READ . An application dated _____________ of __________________________________, R/o __________________________ has requested to grant N.A. Permission in respect of land bearing Survey No. __________________ admeasuring ______________________ of village ____________________ for____________________ purpose. </p><p> The concerned department have reported as under: </p><p> 1 The A.T.P.. Daman vide letter No. No.ATlVDMN/NA/BHI/46(l,2,3)/65/2019 dated 27 062019, has reported that the land in question falls in Urbanisable Zonc-U2, Dimension & arrangement of the plot is adequate for proposed use. The land is not within CRZ. </p><p> 2 The Mamlatdar. Daman vide letter No. MAM/DMN/359 dated 30/09/2019 has reported that the occupant of the land in question is Sliri Sureshchandra Ramanlal Desai, R/o Brahmin Faliyu, Vatar. Vapi. The land is not under litigation/inquiry/disputc etc. Land revenue paid. The land in question is not under acquisition. The land in question falls within cultivable command area of Damanganga Project. </p><p> The land falls in Urbanisable Zone-U2 and direct access is available </p></div><h3 align="center" style="text-decoration: underline;">ORDER</h3> <div> <p> N.A. Permission is hereby granted under Section 32 to the holder __________________________R/o ____________________________________ to convert agriculture land of Survey No ________________admeasuring_________________ of village _________________________________for bonafide _________________ use only with the following conditions:- </p></div><ol> <li>The permission shall be subject to the provision of Goa, Daman & Diu land Revenue Code 196S Rules framed thereunder.</li><li>Holder shall submit a layout plan and get it approved by the Administration within one month before starting any land development or construction work.</li><li>The holder shall commence N.A. use within a period of five year from the date of this order, failing which unless the said period is extended by the Collector from time to time the permission granted shall be deemed to have been lapsed.</li><li> Commencement of N.A. use shall mean actual execution of the project for which permission is granted and in case applicant fails to execute to project within five year, the permission granted shall be cancelled. </li><li> The holder shall send an intimation regarding completion of building within a month after construction work is over. </li><li> The holder shall abide by other reasonable condition or conditions to the use ofthe land. </li><li> Any kind of pathway, right of way. Canal, natural drainage etc. will remain as it is and should not be disturbed after any kind of construction. The rights of general public will remain as it was existing before N.A. and as per Revenue Map. </li><li> Development of the land including road etc. shall be done before putting the land to N.A. use. </li><li> No. tree shall be cut without obtaining prior permission from the Forest Department, if any existing tree on the land is required to be failed. </li><li> As the plot falls within the command area of Damanganga Irrigation Project no construction should come up in alignment of any canal of the Damanganga project passing through the plot </li><li>As the plot falls within the Command area of Damanganga Irrigation Project there should be a setback of 5(five) meters on either side ofthe canal while unit is constructed and water flow shall not be affected.</li><li> Applicant shall not put the land to N.A. use without obtaining Construction Licence and any other NOG permission. If any. required from the Competent Atnbority. </li><li> Applicant shall submit building plan as per DC Rules. 2005 of Daman District and get the lay out plan and building plan approved from Town & Country Planning Department prior to obtained construction licence from the concerned Panchayat </li><li> Building line & Control Line shall be as per the Notification No.P\VDWD-IIDIU20I9- 20 1142 dated 22102019. published in the Official Gazette. Extra Ordinar. No. 41 dated 23/102019. </li><li> The holder shall observe all other Laws Rules in force failing which the permission granted should be revoked cancelled immediately. </li></ol> <table style="width: 100%;"> <tr> <td style="width: 70%;font-size:20px;"></td><td style="width: 30%;font-size:20px;">(Dr. Rakesh Minhas) <br>Collector, Daman. </td></tr><tr></tr></table> <p> To, </p><p> Shri Sureshchandra Ramanlal Desai, </p><p> R/o. Erahim Faliyu, </p><p> Vatar, Vapi </p><ol> Copy along with copy of Sanad forwarded for necessary action to: - <li>The Associate Town Planner, Daman</li><li>The Mamlatdar, Daman</li><li>The Enquiry Officer, City Survey, Daman</li></ol> </div></body></html>';
