mlatdar. Daman vide letter No. MAM/DMN/359 dated 30/09/2019 has reported that the occupant of the land in question is Sliri Sureshchandra Ramanlal Desai, R/o Brahmin Faliyu, Vatar. Vapi. The land is not under litigation/inquiry/disputc etc. Land revenue paid. The land in question is not under acquisition. The land in question falls within cultivable command area of Damanganga Project. </p><p> The land falls in Urbanisable Zone-U2 and direct access is available </p></div><h3 align="center" style="text-decoration: underline;">ORDER</h3> <div> <p> N.A. Permission is hereby granted under Section 32 to the holder  <span style="text-decoration:underline;"> ' . $data["10"] . ' </span>R/o  <span style="text-decoration:underline;"> ' . $data["11"] . ' </span> to convert agriculture land of Survey No  <span style="text-decoration:underline;"> ' . $data["12"] . ' </span>admeasuring <span style="text-decoration:underline;"> ' . $data["13"] . ' </span> of village  <span style="text-decoration:underline;"> ' . $data["15"] . ' </span>for bonafide  <span style="text-decoration:underline;"> ' . $data["16"] . ' </span> use only with the following conditions:- </p></div><ol> <li>The permission shall be subject to the provision of Goa, Daman & Diu land Revenue Code 196S Rules framed thereunder.</li><li>Holder shall submit a layout plan and get it approved by the Administration within one month before starting any land development or construction work.</li><li>The holder shall commence N.A. use within a period of five year from the date of this order, failing which unless the said period is extended by the Collector from time to time the permission granted shall be deemed to have been lapsed.</li><li> Commencement of N.A. use shall mean actual execution of the project for which permission is granted and in case applicant fails to execute to project within five year, the permission granted shall be cancelled. </li><li> The holder shall send an intimation regarding completion of building 