><tr></tr></table> <p> To, </p><p> Shri Sureshchandra Ramanlal Desai, </p><p> R/o. Erahim Faliyu, </p><p> Vatar, Vapi </p><ol> Copy along with copy of Sanad forwarded for necessary action to: - <li>The Associate Town Planner, Daman</li><li>The Mamlatdar, Daman</li><li>The Enquiry Officer, City Survey, Daman</li></ol> </div></body></html>';
